Color Gradients (v3)
	http://stackoverflow.com/questions/13040765/how-to-call-bootstraps-less-gradient-mixins
	http://stackoverflow.com/questions/13436379/rails-with-bootstrap-sass-how-do-you-use-mixins
	Parameters to the gradient mixin are: start-color, end-color, start-percent, end-percent
	body {
	  @include gradient-vertical($white, #08c);
	}